      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "An active market is repotred for\nirrigated land adjacent to Spokane.\nand fruit growers from all over the\ncountry are beginning to realize\nthe superior climatic and soil con-\nditions of the Spokane valley. Lew\nis & Snider state they sold an ag-\ngregate of So acres at Vera yester-\nday to the following buyers:\n\n\nEugene Murray. Palouse, 10\nacres, $4,000: G. w. WATSON, Pa\nlouise, 10 acres. $2.750; G. M. Carey,\nPalouse, 10 acres, $4,000; A. H.\nJoslyn, Palouse. 10 acres, $3.50; j.\nS. Dobie, Potlach, acres, $1,000;\nG. M. Godfrey. Godfrey, Wash. 10\nacres. $4,000. A number of these\ntracts will be improved immediate\nly."
    }
